<li><a href="/wiki/Arthur_S._Link" title="Arthur S. Link">Link, Arthur S.</a> and <a href="/wiki/Richard_L._McCormick" title="Richard L. McCormick" class="mw-redirect">McCormick, Richard L.</a>. <i>Progressivism (American History Series)</i>. Harlan Davidson, 1983. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0882958143" class="internal">ISBN 0-88295-814-3</a></li>
